name: Gather Community Plant #014 - Guandanarian
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their artistic renditions of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Guandanarian is a Polish artist who loves how much freedom there is in creating art. They create both retro and generative pixel art using their hands and pico-8. 

"I want people to slow down and enjoy little things. Literally and figuratively." - Guandanarian
